seo: 锐捷,漏洞检测,CNVD-2021-09650,远程命令执行,RCE
summary: 该插件用于检测锐捷 NBR 路由器是否存在 CNVD-2021-09650 远程命令执行漏洞，通过发送特定请求并验证返回结果来确认漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the Ruijie NBR router has the CNVD-2021-09650 remote command execution vulnerability. It confirms the existence of the vulnerability by sending specific requests and verifying the results.
